Dave, it&#39;s a good approach to having a ruggedized 469 Shack Hack plus
that built-in speaker means you can avoid having to use headphones or
external speakers. In the case of the MegaBox, it&#39;s a more useful
version than just a straight 470 hack since that mixer is integrated.
These incremental improvements are also inspiring for those like me
who like to sketch drawings of the Ultimate Box. -Bill


